  "summary": "Important: libndp security update",
  "details": "Libndp is a library (used by NetworkManager) that provides a wrapper for the IPv6 Neighbor Discovery Protocol. It also provides a tool named ndptool for sending and receiving NDP messages.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* libndp: buffer overflow in route information length field (CVE-2024-5564)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
